Package: hellmer
Title: Batch Processing for Chat Models
Version: 0.1.2
Authors@R: person("Dylan", "Pieper", , "dylanpieper@gmail.com", role =
        c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Batch processing framework for 'ellmer' chat models.
        Provides both sequential and parallel processing of chat
        interactions with features including tool calling and
        structured data extraction. Enables workflow management through
        progress tracking and recovery and automatic retry with
        backoff. Additional quality-of-life features include verbosity
        (or echo) control and sound notifications. Parallel processing
        is implemented via the 'future' framework. Includes methods for
        retrieving progress status, chat texts, and chat objects.
